Package com.here.sdk.search

Class EVChargingStation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.sdk.search.EVChargingStation
  • public final class EVChargingStation
extends java.lang.Object

    Group of connectors for electrical vehicles, defined by a common charging connector type and max power level.

    Use PlaceCategory.BUSINESS_AND_SERVICES_EV_CHARGING_STATION to find stations. In the Details of a Place result you can find the list of found pools containing stations, if any.

    For offline EV rich attributes, also enable LayerConfiguration.Feature.EV in SDKOptions.layerConfiguration.

      • powerFeedTypeName

        @Nullable
public java.lang.String powerFeedTypeName

        Name of the power feed type with respect to https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SAE_J1772#Charging standard. Provides the customer information on the charge level of the specific Connector Type. Also, can describe level that is used in North America and Australia. In that case label 'North America (Australia)' is present. This field can be null if data is unavailable.
